snippet.title: Let's Build a Zoo Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Let's Build a Zoo now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1547890/Lets_Build_a_Zoo/
Sign up to the Steam beta now: https://forms.gle/g1pCdD8vmV4Ge3z29
Join the official Discord: http://discord.gg/letsbuildazoo

It's time to Build a Zoo! Construct and decorate enclosures, buy and breed animals, hire zookeepers and vets... then try your hand at DNA splicing, and stitch together over 300,000 different types of animal. This can only go smoothly...
